toluapp
------------------------------------------
tolua++ is an extension of toLua, a tool to integrate C/C++ code with Lua.
tolua++ includes new features oriented to c++, such as class templates.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.2-1
  libtoluapp-devel-1.0.93-1bl2
  libtoluapp0-1.0.93-1bl2
  lua5.1-5.1.5-3
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.14.5-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  lua-5.3.5-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/LuaDist/toluapp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/LuaDist/toluapp/archive/1.0.93.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack toluapp-1.0.93-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./toluapp-1.0.93-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/toluapp-1.0.93-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/toluapp-1.0.93-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtoluapp0-1.0.93-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtoluapp-devel-1.0.93-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(toluapp)
  /usr/bin/toluapp.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/toluapp.README
  /usr/share/doc/toluapp/COPYRIGHT
  /usr/share/doc/toluapp/README
  /usr/share/doc/toluapp/README-5.1
  /usr/share/doc/toluapp/html/index.html
  /usr/share/doc/toluapp/html/tolua++.html
  /usr/share/doc/toluapp/html/toluapp.gif

(libtoluapp0)
  /usr/bin/cygtoluapp-0.dll

(libtoluapp-devel)
  /usr/include/tolua++.h
  /usr/lib/libtoluapp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/toluapp.pc

